subtitleNullable: Sea level condition in Charleston, South Carolina
descriptionNullable:
### Source

This dataset was taken from ERDDAP at the Asia Pacific Data Research Center which is public data.


### Content

The main items in this dataset are datetime, and sea level observation. Other items do not really necessary since the location is the same (Charleston) and there is no information in depth and sensor type code.
